Package frc.misc

Annotation Type ServerSide

public @interface ServerSide
Marks that the brobot should only use this. There is no functionality here because it is very difficult to implement and would be of trivial benefit. This acts as a marker annotation that tells the programmer when the function/field/class should be called/accessed/used. In this case the DiscordBot server (usually the drive station) should be the accessor of the marked thing.
